    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Just Giving an alternative way to create the file only if doesn't exists using Path and Files.</p>\n\n<pre><code>Path path = Paths.get(\"Some/path/filename.txt\");\nFiles.createDirectories(path.getParent());\nif( !Files.exists(path))\n    Files.createFile(path);\nFiles.write(path, (\"\").getBytes());\n</code></pre>\n"
