  "title" : "Java FileOutputStream Create File if not exists",
  "body" : "<p>Is there a way to use FileOutputStream in a way that if a file (String filename) does not exist, then it will create it?</p>\n\n<pre><code>FileOutputStream oFile = new FileOutputStream(\"score.txt\", false);\n</code></pre>\n"
